{"tid":1038915,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣統促黨總裁帶棺材向行政院長示威，自己卻差點跌入棺材","createTime":"2019-02-27T05:05:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T05:16:49.000Z","uid":38255,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ff477a9f141235cc5dd06d4be7ac381d2009235c","tid":1038915,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T05:05:25.000Z","msg":"行政院長蘇貞昌日前在立法院接受備詢時的「掃把說」，引起中華統一促進黨不滿。統促黨總裁張安樂今早率眾抬棺到立法院外抗議，要送棺材給蘇貞昌，群眾將棺材抬下車時，張安樂卻自己不慎、幾乎跌進棺材裡；警方隨後查扣棺材，張卻一直嚷著「我的棺材」，要向警方討回。警方三度舉牌警告，並針對脫序行為依違反社會秩序維護法裁罰，群眾最後才逐漸散去。<br />\n今天早上10點半，約120名統促黨成員前往立法院中山南路大門，他們還找來一輛貨車載運一口棺材；原本站在貨車上的張安樂大喊「把棺材抬下去」，但群眾抬棺過程中不慎將棺材摔落地面，張安樂也自摔，差點摔進棺材裡。群眾見狀大喊「保護總裁」，場面一度緊張。<br />\n<br />\n不過，警方最後將棺材抬回貨車上，並將棺材查扣；張安樂不滿警方作為，對現場警方大喊「我的棺材！」甚至質疑警方「搶奪」他的棺材。<br />\n警方最後三度對張安樂等群眾舉牌警告，並向他告誡，棺材掉落在地面違反社維法，最後張安樂要求警方「將棺材轉送給蘇貞昌」，聚集的統促黨成員才陸續離去。警方說，其中一名統促黨成員攜帶折疊刀到場遭警方發現，警方將以違反社維法裁罰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6NeehJ7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6NeehJ7.png&h=abaa98c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/marskino/videos/2728151157202668/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmarskino%2Fvideos%2F2728151157202668%2F&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6d5VMZmAwfp0CD4JwUII9h4%3D&h=1034358a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/marskino/videos/2728151157202668/</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e75c37da5ba90fa99f56ae963e8005d8042aff2","tid":1038915,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T05:06:39.000Z","msg":"台狗真係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學下香港啦, 進化到抬紙棺材<br />\n慳水慳力"},{"pid":"98638e188c5864f544753da1047e9f789c43c9b3","tid":1038915,"uid":36901,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T05:07:39.000Z","msg":"車上條友送佢一程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ea1e3503bc1312d55fd71230ac8415f77e2c2e","tid":1038915,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T05:07:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012e2c9da081990187720d9bb6812f1a418a9c1e","tid":1038915,"uid":10757,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T05:10:32.000Z","msg":"白狼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係型到仆街"},{"pid":"fc232fb46aa8803504f3a85662973a4222726fe3","tid":1038915,"uid":238370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T05:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2546e29ae04df94b705da5e5b068cc4bab23d79e","tid":1038915,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T05:13:47.000Z","msg":"呢個乜水？"},{"pid":"187845da089cbc6a62a452df850a5977975092de","tid":1038915,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T05:14:02.000Z","msg":"白狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6f01d3365daf6c4e8a5544473da5d17379d6e1","tid":1038915,"uid":63870,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T05:16:49.000Z","msg":"張安樂不滿警方作為，對現場警方大喊「我的棺材！」甚至質疑警方「搶奪」他的棺材。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/so